      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/jeep-hero.jpg" alt="Used Jeep auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Used Jeep Parts for Sale</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral. Jeep owners don’t just drive — they explore. At PartsCentral, we help keep that adventure alive with OEM used Jeep parts that are tested, trail-ready, and shipped nationwide. From Wranglers to Grand Cherokees, we’ve got your Jeep auto parts covered — ruggedly and reliably.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral.</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>OEM used Jeep parts tested for durability</li><li>Trail-ready components built for adventure</li><li>Nationwide shipping across the United States</li><li>Designed to keep Jeep capability alive</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Made for Drivers Who Live Bold</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Jeep drivers crave capability, durability, and freedom to go wherever the road or trail leads. Whether it’s your weekend off-roader or daily workhorse, your Jeep deserves authentic performance. That’s why our used Jeep parts are built to last, OEM-tested, and ready for any terrain.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Jeep Parts We Carry</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Engines, transmissions, transfer cases</li><li>Axles, driveshafts, suspension components</li><li>Radiators, fans, AC compressors</li><li>Doors, fenders, bumpers, grilles</li><li>Starters, alternators, batteries</li><li>Control arms, steering racks, knuckles</li><li>Headlights, taillights, interior switches</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Trail-Tested. Mechanic-Approved.</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Every used Jeep auto part we offer is inspected for strength, safety, and long-haul performance. Our expert team checks for real-world reliability so you get parts that work and last.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Save Big. Drive Far.</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">New Jeep parts can cost a fortune. Our OEM used Jeep auto parts deliver the same trusted performance at a fraction of the cost. Get a fast, free quote with no sign-ups or stress. We’ll reply in minutes and ship quickly.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Jeep Models We Support</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">We carry used Jeep auto parts for nearly every model. Can’t find your model? We’ll help you source it.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>Jeep Cherokee</li><li>Jeep Commander</li><li>Jeep Compass</li><li>Jeep Gladiator</li><li>Jeep Grand Cherokee</li><li>Jeep Liberty</li><li>Jeep Patriot</li><li>Jeep Renegade</li><li>Jeep Wagoneer</li><li>Jeep Wrangler</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Jeep Drivers Trust PartsCentral</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Rigorous quality inspections</li><li>Nationwide shipping</li><li>Competitive pricing</li><li>Secure checkout and easy returns</li><li>Prompt customer support available 7 days a week</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Get Your Jeep Trail-Ready Again</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Just search your model, request a quote, and order online in minutes. Join Jeep drivers across the country who trust PartsCentral for dependable, affordable, and adventure-ready used Jeep parts.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Request a free quote today.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Used Jeep Parts for Sale<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Used Jeep Parts for Sale<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)] transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-95">Find My Parts</a></div></section><section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 bg-[#07142B] text-[#E8F3FF]"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-orbitron mb-10 text-center">USED <!-- -->JEEP<!-- --> AUTO PARTS</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><ul class="space-y-2 text-lg leading-7 font-jaldi list-disc list-inside text-[#cecece]"><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Engine Assembly</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Transmission</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS Control Module</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS System (Anti-Lock)</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor Clutch</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Condenser</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Evaporator</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Air Bag Control Module</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Air Cleaner Box</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Air Flow Meter</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Air Injection Pump</li><li>Jeep<!-- --> <!-- -->Alternator</li>